divs: Sighting DetailsI was trying a new camera and took some photos of the sky the day before and photographed airplanes passing above my balcony. The next day I was at the balcony smoking a cigarette and saw this light coming from south to north over the sea to my left (East). I grabbed the camera and took 3 photos, it was fast. I downloaded and what I saw was just a smudge, but I saw something odd! I'm attaching the pictures maybe with some software you can see it better, Thanks.
